OL,5, US basketball star Kyrie Irving has    
OL,6, apologised after he was suspended by   
OL,7, his club, the Brooklyn Nets, amid      
OL,8, allegations of anti-Semitism.          
OL,10,FThe star received a five-game ban after
OL,11,Fhe defended his decision to post a link
OL,12,Fto a documentary that has been         
OL,13,Fcriticised as anti-Semitic on Twitter. 
OL,15,FIn a statement posted to Instagram,    
OL,16,FIrving said he was "deeply sorry" for  
OL,17,Fthe "hurt and pain" he had caused.     
OL,19,F"I am learning from this unfortunate   
OL,20,Fevent," he added.                      
